appears that they have stepped up patrols at the local runs. Thefts appear to be classic 'snatch &<br/>
grab' as Johnny Law calls them so they ain't professional theives by any means. Just a heads up for<br/>
those that frequent the areas.....hide your valuables or better yet, leave 'em at home. </div>
